---
---
<section class="bg-[#fafafa]">
  <!-- Testimonial header -->
  <div class="px-section" style="padding-left:120px;padding-right:120px;">
    <div class="bg-white border-l border-r border-[#e5e5e5] flex items-center justify-between p-10">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-medium text-[32px] text-[#0a0a0a] leading-[1.1] whitespace-nowrap" style="letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Hear from our satisfied clients</h2>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <button class="btn-secondary w-9 h-9 rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 12L6 8l4-4"/></svg>
        </button>
        <button class="btn-secondary w-9 h-9 rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 12l4-4-4-4"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Testimonial card -->
  <div class="bg-[#fafafa] border-t border-b border-[#e5e5e5] px-section" style="padding-left:120px;padding-right:120px;">
    <div class="bg-white border border-[#e5e5e5] p-10">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-w-[540px]">
          <!-- Logo -->
          <div class="h-10 flex items-center">
            <img src="/assets/99c36766b0268bc5518ab5033d37db5518a3c1aa.png" alt="Warmly" class="h-6 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <!-- Quote -->
          <p class="font-body font-normal text-[18px] text-[#0a0a0a] leading-[1.5]" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">
            "We had zero Salesforce development experience, but still launched a fully functional managed package within a week. The platform made the process incredibly simple - no code, no waiting on engineers. Total game-changer."
          </p>
          <!-- Attribution -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-body font-normal text-[14px] text-[#0a0a0a] leading-[1.5]">Max Greenwald</span>
            <span class="font-body font-normal text-[12px] text-[#737373] leading-[1.5]">CEO, Warmly</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="testimonial-photo flex-shrink-0" style="height:280px;aspect-ratio:1;">
          <img src="/assets/a374d130303717255230df1a00963737f45bdc2e.png" alt="Max Greenwald" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
